Q.40 Create a table customer_Details which stores the EmailID & password of the customer .EmailID is primary key.
     Create a Dynamic Project using Maven. There is a Customer class(Entity Class) which has emailID and Password as fields.
     Create a DAO class which sets the Email ID and Password in the table through the object of Customer class.
     Create a Servlet which displays the Email Ids of all cusomers.
    
=>

//form.jsp

<html>
<body>
<form action="servass_40" method="get">
ENTER EMAIL : <input type="text" name="em">
ENTER PASSWORD : <input type="text" name="pas"> 
<input type="submit" value="Enter">
</form>

